      <title>匈牙利随着经济形式扩展从债券到银行的干预</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/hungary-expands-meddling-from-bonds-to-banks-as-economy-stutters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利将其干预措施扩大到从债券基金到银行业的领域，因为政府在去年的衰退之后寻求恢复增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/hungary-expands-meddling-from-bonds-to-banks-as-economy-stutters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 12:01:47 GMT</pubDate>
