      <title>挪威在北极的约翰·卡斯伯格球场开始石油生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/norway-begins-oil-production-at-johan-castberg-field-in-arctic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威的860亿克罗纳（81亿美元）约翰·卡斯伯格（Johan Castberg）在巴伦特海（Barents Sea）开始抽水，这是该国北极水域运营的第二个主要领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/norway-begins-oil-production-at-johan-castberg-field-in-arctic</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 11:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
