      <title>津巴布韦的主要城市遭受了抗议活动的痛苦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/business-suffers-in-zimbabwe-s-major-cities-amid-call-for-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[津巴布韦的首都哈拉雷（Harare）及其第二城市布拉瓦约（Bulawayo）在周一安静，尽管呼吁抗议南部非洲国家领导人。]]></description>
