      <title>铀市场冻结，关税威胁嘎嘎作响的买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/uranium-market-freezes-as-tariff-threats-rattle-would-be-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税威胁会慢慢购买并延迟新合同，北美铀市场正在停顿，因为美国核电站吓到了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/uranium-market-freezes-as-tariff-threats-rattle-would-be-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 10:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
