      <title>雷诺，日产汽车在联盟放松中的更多股票销售额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/renault-nissan-open-door-to-more-share-sales-in-alliance-tweak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷诺SA和日产汽车公司同意进一步放松他们的长期联盟，为更多的股票销售铺平了道路，因为日本汽车制造商仍承受着建立财务状况的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/renault-nissan-open-door-to-more-share-sales-in-alliance-tweak</guid>
